      "heading": null,
      "description": "Preheat the oven to 200°C."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Tear the mushrooms into 1-2cm small chunks and place onto a baking tray. Drizzle with oil and season generously with salt. Roast for 20-25 mins, until golden."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Trim and finely mince the red chilli and garlic. Thinly slice the spring onions, pick the mint leaves."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
